➜“亚裔女性+中国背景”，拜登政府的新贸易代表是什么来头？
http://www.sohu.com/a/437438354_237556	29799
<div id="sohuplayer">
<script type="text/javascript" src="//tv.sohu.com/upload/swf/showVrsPlayer.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
showVrsPlayer({
bid:'227585757',
width: '500',
height: '375',
